<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TOGAPhotos 审核队列积压提醒</title>
</head>

<body
        style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f6f7f9; font-family: Segoe UI, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1f;">
<div style="width: 100%; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 16px 12px; box-sizing: border-box;">
    <div style="width: 100%;">

        <section
                style="padding: 20px 18px; background: #ffffff; box-shadow: none; border: 0; display: block; letter-spacing: 0.01em;">
            <div style="display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                <div style="display: block;">
                    <div>
                        <img src="https://cos-125-tp-cdn.794td.cn/assets/n_logo_b.jpg" alt="TOGAPhotos" width="120"
                             style="display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;">
                    </div>
                    <div style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 8px;">
                        审核队列积压提醒</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="height: 1px; width: 100%; background: rgba(12, 12, 13, 0.08);"></div>
            <article
                    style="margin: 16px 0; padding: 20px 22px; border-left: 2px solid #ff4d4f; background: #fff8f8; color: #1c1c1f; letter-spacing: 0.01em;">
                <div style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.4;">
                    当前有 <span style="color: #ff4d4f;">{{count}}</span> 张照片在队列中超过5天未审核
                </div>
                <div style="color: #545454; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 6px;">
                    以下照片的 <code style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, monospace;">screener_1</code> 仍为空，请尽快安排审核。
                </div>
            </article>
            <div style="display: block;">
                {{#each photos}}
                    <article
                            style="margin: 12px 0 0 0; padding: 16px 20px; border-left: 2px solid #faad14; background: #ffffff; color: #1c1c1f; box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.05); letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; align-items: start; gap: 12px;">
                        <div style="display: block; min-width: 60px;">
                            <div style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7a7a7a;">
                                图片 ID</div>
                            <div style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.3;">{{id}}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: block; flex: 1;">
                            <div style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7a7a7a;">
                                图片信息</div>
                            <div style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #1c1c1f;">
                                航空公司：{{airline}}</div>
                            <div style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #1c1c1f;">
                                注册号：{{ac_reg}}</div>
                            <div style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #545454; margin-top: 4px;">
                                上传者：{{username}}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: block; text-align: right;">
                            <div style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7a7a7a;">
                                等待时间</div>
                            <div
                                    style="display: inline-block; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(250, 173, 20, 0.14); color: #9c6100;">
                                {{daysInQueue}} 天</div>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                {{/each}}
            </div>
            <a href="https://dash.togaphotos.com"
               style="display: block; width: 80%; margin: 20px auto 4px; padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(43, 123, 255, 0.12); color: #1a4ea2; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-decoration: none; text-align: center;">
                前往审核队列
            </a>
            <div style="height: 1px; width: 100%; background: rgba(12, 12, 13, 0.08); margin-top: 16px;"></div>
            <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #8a8a8a; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 8px;">
                此邮件由系统自动发送，请勿直接回复。如有疑问请联系 support@togaphotos.com
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>
</body>

</html>
